Package: libsquish-dev
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: @MAINTAINER@
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/squish-compression/squish
Depends: libsquish1 (= @VERSION@)
Description: context-mixing compressor — development files
 Header, static library, versioned .so symlink, and pkg-config file for building
 and linking against libsquish (-lsquish, or pkg-config squish).
 .
 SQUISH is a context-mixing file compressor shipped as a linkable C library with
 a command-line tool.
